data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 5.05-acre estate in Mico, TX, a sanctuary offering luxurious living, hill country views, and the freedom of no HOA or city taxes. The main residence showcases high ceilings and a versatile loft area upstairs, perfect for a home office or entertainment space. Multiple balconies provide panoramic vistas of the surrounding natural beauty. The well-designed kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring ample counter space and modern conveniences. Step outside to discover an outdoor kitchen set against the backdrop of sweeping hill country landscapes, ideal for alfresco dining and entertaining. As an added bonus, the property includes a fully equipped (744 sqft) casita, perfect for guests or potential rental income. Located just minutes from San Antonio, this estate offers the tranquility of country living with the convenience of city amenities nearby. Don't miss this rare and exceptional opportunity; schedule your private tour today!
